stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PricingRequested

    %% =========================
    %% INPUT VALIDATION
    %% =========================
    PricingRequested --> ValidateInputs: Validate pickup, dropoff, ride_type
    ValidateInputs --> InputsInvalid: Missing or invalid data
    ValidateInputs --> BaseFareCalculation: Inputs valid

    InputsInvalid --> PricingFailed
    PricingFailed --> [*]

    %% =========================
    %% BASE FARE CALCULATION
    %% =========================
    BaseFareCalculation --> CalculateDistance: Compute estimated distance
    CalculateDistance --> CalculateTime: Estimate duration
    CalculateTime --> ApplyRideTypeRates: Apply ride_type pricing rules

    ApplyRideTypeRates --> BaseFareComputed

    %% =========================
    %% SURGE CALCULATION
    %% =========================
    BaseFareComputed --> FetchSupplyDemand: Get active drivers & requests
    FetchSupplyDemand --> ComputeDemandRatio: demand / supply ratio
    ComputeDemandRatio --> SurgeDecision

    SurgeDecision --> SurgeNotRequired: ratio <= threshold
    SurgeDecision --> SurgeRequired: ratio > threshold

    SurgeNotRequired --> SurgeMultiplierSet: multiplier = 1.0
    SurgeRequired --> ApplySurgeFormula: Calculate surge multiplier
    ApplySurgeFormula --> CapSurge: Apply surge cap (max limit)

    CapSurge --> SurgeMultiplierSet

    %% =========================
    %% FINAL PRICE
    %% =========================
    SurgeMultiplierSet --> FinalFareComputed: final_fare = base_fare * multiplier

    FinalFareComputed --> PricingResponseReady
    PricingResponseReady --> [*]